name: Chakra Pendants
description: The pendants could be used as a necklace, bracelet, earrings, really anything a patron could imagine! They are hand made from Alder wood grown in the USA and are suitable for both men and women. Each of the 7 pendants represent one individual Chakra symbol contained in the package of seven, each engraved with their Chakra name on it , along with a little description of each of there meanings
